        <div class="faq-a">You can't prevent all lean mass loss, but you can dramatically reduce it. The two primary protective strategies are maintaining high daily protein intake (1.2–1.6g/kg) and continuing resistance training throughout your GLP-1 treatment. Tracking protein daily is critical because appetite suppression makes it easy to under-eat protein without realizing it.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
