        <div class="faq-a">Significant muscle loss leads to slower metabolism, reduced strength, higher risk of falls and injury, greater difficulty maintaining weight loss long-term, and accelerated aging effects. For men over 40, protecting muscle mass isn't vanity — it's directly linked to mobility, independence, and healthspan.</div>
